  <!-- Hero / Overview -->
  <section id="overview" class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-14">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6">The World of Labubu — Where Mischief Meets Magic</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Born from the imagination of Hong Kong artist <strong>Kasing Lung</strong> and produced by <strong>POP MART</strong>, Labubu has become one of the most beloved art toy characters in the world. With its pointy ears, mischievous grin, and timeless childlike energy, Labubu stands as a symbol of creativity, innocence, and joy.
    </p>
    <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
      Each edition tells a different story — from playful adventures to moments of quiet reflection. The series spans seasonal lines, artist collaborations, and special event releases, all united by a singular design language that is instantly recognizable yet endlessly expressive.
    </p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <figure>
        <img src="https://cdn.i-scmp.com/sites/default/files/d8/images/canvas/2024/12/24/857a7e60-2a86-4b91-88c0-f3e650f68384_7a554a82.jpg" alt="Labubu art toy showcase photo" class="rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-neutral-200">
