    <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      <strong>Labubu Hope</strong> embodies warmth and optimism. With soft tones and a peaceful expression, Hope is a quiet reminder that light can still break through uncertainty. In 360°, textures, contours, and micro‑details become part of the storytelling — transforming a figure into an intimate art experience.
    </p>
    <p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Tip: View in a bright room with indirect light; if you’re on mobile, rotate the phone to landscape for a wider viewport.
