  <!-- Collector Guide -->
  <section id="guide" class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-14">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Collector’s Guide — Buying & Authenticity</h3>
    <ul class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed list-disc pl-5">
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>Boxes & COA:</strong> Keep original packaging and any certificates; they help maintain long‑term value.</li>
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>Release Info:</strong> Verify edition names, release windows, and paint variants before purchasing.</li>
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>Condition:</strong> Inspect for paint transfers or factory marks; minor variations are common in hand‑finished toys.</li>
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>Community:</strong> Join collector forums/groups for trade references and photo comparisons.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

